Note: The Windows files listed above are the same as those listed 
in the Security Bulletin HPSBMA02121 SSRT061157 rev.2.

The installation instructions are in the '.txt' files. For HP-UX, IBM AIX, 
Linux, and Solaris the '.txt' files are contained in the '.shar' files.

The files listed above are available by contacting HP Support as well as 
from the ftp site. Sixty days after the initial release of this Security Bulletin
the files will be removed from the web site. After that please contact 
HP Support to obtain the files.

MANUAL ACTIONS: Yes - NonUpdate
Download and install the files as discussed in the Resolution section.

